PrecisAmendment to Order in Council P.C. 1998-2111 of December 1, 1998 appointing MICHEL FOURNIER, of St-Jean-sur-Richelieu, Quebec, as president of The Federal Bridge Corporation Limited, by replacing the words "for a term of three years" with the words "for a term of five years".
